Remarks

The MemoryCacheSettingsCollection class represents the collection of configuration elements and settings that configure an instance of the MemoryCache class. In other words, this settings collection contains objects that represent elements and settings that are children of a memoryCache element. The MemoryCacheSettingsCollection class contains a namedCaches element.

For more information about the configuration options that are related to this class, see <memoryCache> Element (Cache Settings) and <namedCaches> Element (Cache Settings).
